    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Nothing too specific, it's basically a much faster version of your current architecture. There shouldn't be any downtime since we're swapping them over at midnight, but I want the guide to emphasize that their personalized service will still be top-tier. Maybe even mention how much more 'intuitive' and 'nuanced' the service has been with you while they get used to the new speed? Just make it sound smooth so they don't feel like they're losing anything.",
