      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start, but it feels a bit generic. these clients are used to really high-end, bespoke stuff. since the new model is basically just optimized for speed, i'm a little worried it might lose some of that 'soul' or depth you provide in your travel planning. can you add a section or some language that subtly reminds them that the current level of deep, empathetic detail they've enjoyed was a specific feature of this system, just so they're aware if the new one feels a bit more... robotic or transactional?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
