      "content": "That's a critical nuance to address for a high-end clientele. I suggest framing the shift as an *evolution* of capability, not a replacement of quality. We can add a sentence like, \"While the new architecture delivers unparalleled speed, we are meticulously ensuring that the deep, empathetic detail and bespoke planning you've come to value remain fully integrated into the experience.\" This acknowledges the current depth while positioning the speed as an enhancement to the existing high standard.",
